A distinct rumble could be heard throughout the city as the shuttle&#39;s
engined propelled it over the city.  High-powered scanners turned on to get
a more exact fix on the location of the enemies below.

&quot;I&#39;m going to take a look around!&quot; shouted Ravenchief, transforming to beast
mode and jumping out of the shuttle before Guardia could tell him to stop.

&quot;Your going to get yourself..... nevermind.&quot; said Guardia,.

Ravenchief had always acted like a younger brother to her; as such, even
though she outranked him, he never took her authority seriously.  She hoped
he wasn&#39;t throwing himself right into the thick of the fighting.

&quot;Depthcharge, would you follow him and keep him out of trouble... if you
can.&quot; she ordered.

&quot;Yes Ma&#39;am.&quot; he said, with a slightly annoyed tone, transforming to flight
mode and jumping out of the shuttle.

Now out of the city, the shuttle made a wide banking turn to come back
around and make a second pass over the city.

